<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="be-on-the-phone">(be) on the phone</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在打电话：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My husband answered the door while I was on the phone in the dining room.
我正在餐厅打电话时， 我丈夫去开了门。</p><footer>2019 天津改</footer></div></div>